-- African Barrick Gold Mulls Acquisitions, Plans Tanzania Listing, CEO Says
-- Thomas Biesheuvel
-- 2010-06-22T08:41:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-22/african-barrick-gold-mulls-acquisitions-plans-tanzania-listing-ceo-says.html

          
          
             African Barrick Gold Ltd. Chief
Executive Officer Greg Hawkins said the company has an
“appetite” for acquisitions, adding that its first steps
outside Tanzania will be “very carefully” taken.  
 African Barrick Gold hopes to list in Dar Es Salaam,
Tanzania, by the end of the year, Hawkins said today at a
conference in London.  
